msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Attached to the note is... some form of data storage drive. Deciphering it "
"shows information on... some form of cleansing ritual. It will only work "
"once - you will have to pick which ghost you want to bring back to "
"cognizance, the rest will, however, be able to be put to rest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:672
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pick Frostwall."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:674
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You and your crew hold a brief ritual, and Frostwall manifests before your "
"eyes, rubbing his head. \"You... you saved me! From this day onwards... I "
"will fight by your side, Captain, to the end of the Multiverse!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:675
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[1]/event/crewMember"
