msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Pick Deathbloom."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:685
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You and your crew hold a brief ritual, and Deathbloom manifests before your "
"eyes, flourishing her petals. \"Hahaaa, now that's what I'm talking about! "
"C'mon, Renegade... there's always gonna be more places to discover, more "
"treasure to find.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:686
