msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:716
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Pick Leo."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:718
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You and your crew hold a brief ritual, and Leo manifests before your eyes, "
"finally mustering the courage to speak. \"Mercy? After everything... you "
"still want me to... live? Renegade. Consider me a true friend, then!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:719
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[5]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Leo"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:721
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:727
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Pick Searak."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:729
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You and your crew hold a brief ritual, and Searak manifests before your "
"eyes, robes flapping proudly in a nonexistent wind. \"In all of my years of "
"service, to any cause, I have never seen the kind of courage you've "
"displayed today. If I make it back home, every Duskbringer who will ever "
"live will sing of your deeds today!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:730
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[6]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Searak"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml:732
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_chaotic_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_CREW_CHAOS_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[6]/event/choice/text"
